msgid "拼版入口示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:17
msgid "点击创建拼版单元，然后鼠标框选绘制主板区域。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst
msgid "拼版主板绘制示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:25
msgid "手动新建："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:24
msgid "可以点击列表中的 “添加图标” 逐个添加子板，然后切换至选择工具，用鼠标拖拽调整位置。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:25
msgid "适用于不规则或特殊拼版场景。"
