msgid "删除拼版单元示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:43
msgid "参数继承与同步原则"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:45
msgid "默认情况下，所有子板的检测参数（如 ROI、阈值、检测项）均继承主板设置，并且子板上的检测框不可编辑"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:53
msgid "通过“同步 ROI”选项："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst
msgid "同步 ROI 设置示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:52
msgid "（默认开启）开启时，主板调整会同步到所有子板。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:53
msgid "关闭后，可在每个子板单独调整该元件的 ROI，适用于局部差异或特殊需求。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:56
msgid "数据管理："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:56
msgid "数据集自动按元件分组，统计所有子板的检测结果。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:59
msgid "条形码检测工具"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:61
msgid "支持在拼版场景下识别每个子板的序列号、批次号等条码信息。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:67
msgid "操作流程："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:65
msgid "在模板编辑器中，先为主板添加条形码检测框，并分组为新元件。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:66
msgid "创建拼版后，系统会自动将该条形码检测框复制到所有子板。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:67
msgid "检测时，系统可分别识别每个子板上的条码内容，并自动作为序列号归档。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:69
msgid "应用场景：追溯生产批次、定位异常子板、自动分组统计。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:71
msgid "判废板阈值设置"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:73
msgid ""
"可在系统配置中为拼版设置整体判废板阈值。参考 :ref:`系统JSON配置`，编辑 "
"wasted_array_board_failure_ratio 参数并保存。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/pcb_array.rst:74
msgid "检测过程中，若任一子板的元件 NG 率超过该阈值，则该子板会被判定为废板并报出。"
msgstr ""

